---
layout: base.njk
title: Senior Software Engineer & Pluralsight Author
description: I help engineering teams move from "It works on my machine" to "It works at scale."
---

<section class="mb-24">
  <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
    <img src="images/profile.png" alt="Pietro Cascio" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover ring-1 ring-gray-200">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-black leading-tight">
        {{ title }}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium">Create. Break. Fix. Repeat.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
    Hi, I'm <strong>Pietro</strong> (but my teams call me <strong>Piero</strong>). <br>
    I help engineering teams move from "It works on my machine" to "It works at scale." My work focuses on Java, Spring Boot, and dismantling Hype-Driven Development.
  </p>
</section>
<section class="mb-20">
  <h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-gray-400 uppercase mb-8 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
    // Engineering Philosophy
  </h2>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-800">
    <div class="flex items-start">
      <span class="mr-3 text-gray-400">➔</span>
      <p><strong>Complexity is the enemy.</strong> If you can't explain the architecture on a
        napkin, it's too complex.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start">
      <span class="mr-3 text-gray-400">➔</span>
      <p><strong>Boring technology is better.</strong> We choose stability over resume-padding.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start">
      <span class="mr-3 text-gray-400">➔</span>
      <p><strong>Skepticism as a service.</strong> I critique "silver bullet" solutions before
        they enter your codebase.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="mb-24">
  <h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-gray-400 uppercase mb-8 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
    // Selected Analysis
  </h2>

  {%- for post in collections.post -%}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="group block mb-8">
    <div class="border-l-2 border-gray-100 pl-6 group-hover:border-black transition-colors duration-300">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-purple-700 transition-colors">
        {{ post.data.title }}
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-2">
        {{ post.data.description }}
      </p>
      <div class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">
        Read Analysis &rarr;
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
</section>